# Service Validation Checklist

- Frontend loads without blocking runtime errors.
- Backend responds to expected API health/status calls.
- API/chatbot service is reachable and returns valid responses.
- Reverse proxy routes requests to correct upstream services.
- No failing/unhealthy containers remain after rollout.
- Validate key user flows, not only health endpoints.
